OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mervyn
OL,4,CKersh
OL,6,FMervyn Kersh, Age 98, Royal Army
OL,7,FOrdnance Corps
OL,9,FInterviewed 4 July 2023
OL,11,FLanding on Gold beach three days after
OL,12,FD-Day, Mervyn Kersh was a private
OL,13,Fhelping to ensure that the advancing
OL,14,FBritish Army had enough vehicles to
OL,15,Fwin the battle for Normandy and push
OL,16,Fon into France and the occupied Low
OL,17,FCountries.
OL,19,FHe said: "The first batch of
OL,20,Freconnaissance were all killed on the
OL,21,Fway over, they were torpedoed.
