OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mervyn
OL,4,CKersh
OL,6,F"So they asked for volunteers to take
OL,7,Ftheir place. So I went on my own on
OL,8,Fany ship that was going looking for a
OL,9,Fsuitable site. Which I did find.
OL,11,F"A lovely chateau with room for 1,000
OL,12,Fvehicles and 200 men, the drivers.
OL,14,F"As soon as the engineers had cleared
OL,15,Fall the booby traps an Colonel came
OL,16,Falong and told me to clear off because
OL,17,FI was a private. But then the unit
OL,18,Fcame and we found somewhere in Bayeux.
