OL,4,CKersh
OL,6,F"And we set up business supplying any
OL,7,Funit that lost vehicles which was of
OL,8,Fcourse all the time.
OL,10,F"It continued throughout the war."
OL,12,FThe job was to ensure his team always
OL,13,Fhad 1000 vehicles roadworthy and ready
OL,14,Fto go - replacing those constantly
OL,15,Flost in action or in accidents.
OL,17,FHe said: "Many of the ships that
OL,18,Flanded shed vehicles of all kinds.
OL,19,FAnything from folded bicycles to a
OL,20,Fforty eight-wheel tank transporter.
