OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Mervyn
OL,4,CKersh
OL,6,F"I wasn't a driver but I soon learned
OL,7,Fto drive and I have never had a test
OL,8,Fsince. Still driving. But we had to
OL,9,Fsupply everything.
OL,11,F"It was something I had waited for a
OL,12,Flong, long time.
OL,14,F"A couple of years at least. And
OL,15,Feventually it came and I was delighted
OL,16,Fto be in it."
